FY 2026 funding decrease due to FY 2025 being the last year of funding for Project C97 in support of EAGLE-M development and
continued development of ALT-PNT capabilities to enable precise navigation and timing during MDO operations in the absence of
GPS by leveraging ALT-NAV and VBN efforts.
