Description: Data Processing & Analytics, formerly titled Data Exploitation, ensures the Overhead Persistent Infrared (OPIR)
enterprise can exploit, fuse, and operationalize proliferated sensor data at scale. This thrust develops automated ground
processing, artificial intelligence and machine learning tools, and resilient Development, Security, Operations (DevSecOps)

