detection, extraction, and typing algorithms from ground environments to on-orbit compute architectures to reduce latency,
decrease bandwidth demands, and enable faster decision timelines. By distributing analytics across space and ground segments
and transitioning capabilities into the Future Operationally Resilient Ground Evolution (FORGE) framework, this effort strengthens
