Data Processing & Analytics will continue delivery of operationally contributing Wide Field of View (WFOV) Geosynchronous
Earth Orbit (GEO) wideband data to end users in multiple mission areas and explore transition of capabilities to operations and
sustainment on Future Operationally Resilient Ground Evolution (FORGE). WFOV GEO remains a valuable source of next
