FY 2026 Plans:
RDS will use FY26 ($0.115M) funding for the addressing radio interoperability to support the Net Ready KPP and continue
activities to support follow-on operational test and evaluation (FOT&E).
FY 2025 to FY 2026 Increase/Decrease Statement:
FY26 funds decrease supports scope of requirements for testing in FY26, completing scheduled interoperability activities.
