survivability.
FY 2026 Plans:
FY 2026 research, development, test and evaluation (RDT&E) funds in the amount of $2.070 million supports but is not limited
to the continuation of the software integration and testing of four DDREX Engineering Development Models (EDMs) in support of
Capability Set #1 and Capability Set #2.
FY 2025 to FY 2026 Increase/Decrease Statement:
FY 2026 funding decrease due to transitioning from development to integration and addressing software issues for Capability Sets
