and their effectiveness against various threats. Develop semi-autonomous intelligent friendly forces (BLUFOR) and Opposing
Forces (OPFOR) capable of training Large Scale Combat Operations in support of training Offensive, Defensive and Stability
Operations. Develops appropriate doctrine at scenario specific levels of proficiency, adapting to BLUFOR/OPFOR behaviors, and
reducing exercise overhead in comparison to human run BLUFOR/OPFOR. Develop simulation capable of depicting current and
