home-station availability and distributed collective training to the point of need. NGC will continue to expand and test its cloud
infrastructure and host a production environment capable of supporting over 100 Warfighters, CTCs and Home-station exercises
at scale.
--NGC Software Maintenance: Supports cybersecurity updates to boost cybersecurity posture and fix vulnerabilities, software bug
fixes to resolve reported issues of deployed software, vendor application interoperability changes to support minor improvements
to enable applications to interface with each other and help desk support to fielded software.


