FY 2026 to FY 2027 Increase/Decrease Statement:
FY 2027 Funding increase:
STE -SW (TSS/TMT & NGC): Funding increase will expedite development and delivery of NGC capabilities across all warfighting
functions and multidomain effects. This includes develop and integration of intelligence data feeds to simulate information from
various sources, including satellite collections, radar systems, aircraft, and human intelligence. This allows the system to create a
