A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
There is no FY2027 funding request for this project.

 The Future Interceptor will defend against current and emerging missile, and hypersonic threats in the ballistic missile defense battlespace. The Future Interceptor
 increases Air and Missile Defense (AMD) capability through improved velocity, altitude, and maneuverability characteristics. Requested funding will be used to continue
 hardware/software design and development and procurement of parts of qualified vendors to begin building and testing of critical component prototypes.

