The ARAT CR8 program performs Basic Research to enhance the EW Eco System to support current and future systems under this portfolio. ARAT CR8 will focus
technical strategies that reduce mission data development timelines from detection of a change or new threat to creating and testing a software solution then utilize the
ARAT mission software distribution portal to support forward deployed combat forces.




