FY27 funding will continue to support the development and integration of key software modules for: command and control
of COTS hardware prototypes, algorithms for processing sensor data to verify accuracy of programming, and a user-friendly
graphical user interface (GUI) to visualize data and manage RF Technical Effects operations. The Army will fund a Federally




